'''''-inqua''''' is a [[Quenya]] adjectival ending, seen in '''alcarinqua''' "glorious"<ref>{{WJ|Quendi}}, p. 412</ref> from '''alcar''' "glory". Etymologically, '''-inqua''' means "-full", like "glory-full" in this case.

